Package: TensorPLS
Type: Package
Title: an R package for exploring patterns in three-way omics data using N-PLS-DA
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alessandro", "Giordano", email = "alegiordano@unisa.it", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Toolkit for reading, preprocessing, and constructing tensors 
from omics data, with modeling and feature selection based on Partial Least Squares (PLS) algorithms.
